Text: @shipjolly can you give me Angel 004-017 (digital) link plz...

^

Assuming, from the issue numbers you gave, that you mean the 2000-2001 Dark Horse run, only the first story arc ("Surrogates", issues 1 thru 3) has been re-released digitally so far, as far as I'm aware. The rest is bound to follow at some point - patience! :)
